{"tid":2454072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：民主派應積極表現自己為真正愛國者","createTime":"2021-03-20T03:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T04:03:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c448f14594ff87e3d3d155ef61dc96680c5dc293","tid":2454072,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"湯家驊表示，若修改選舉制度後，立法會內的直選議席減少，造成的觀感是對香港的民意代表不重視，令國際及港人有負面觀感。他又指，選委會大幅增加人數，對短時間內是否能夠有大量有才之士加入參與政府管治工作有憂慮，又認為民主派不應對號入座，指自己是不愛國，因而無責任或能力加入特區管治架構，認為有關想法是錯，指他們應積極表現自己是真正的愛國者，有能力參與及改善本港管治質素，而不是指自己參政空間被收窄。對於資格審查委員會的組成，湯家驊指，委員應要對本港政治及法律，特別是憲法有相當認識，亦要中立及可信性高，以及可能要有對國家安全有研究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383812&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=41191abf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383812</a>"},{"pid":"a66f4cd0c123303a69d3f2c6cde2d3eece62c95a","tid":2454072,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"11哥表現得愛幻幻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CL6Tz93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCL6Tz93.jpg&h=149944a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8358f1f890dd4e67898094c04bd7ee9269c314f","tid":2454072,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"當日初選都話睇唔到有犯國安法<br />\n11哥根本無料到"},{"pid":"99f0cf906ac331c0d835461eb1c5a400ab3f6e71","tid":2454072,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:58:08.000Z","msg":"梁家傑：我有話對湯家驊說<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2039434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2039434</a><br />\n雖然你已脫離捍衛法治的隊伍，但我們一眾同業毋忘初衷，更多法律界新晉決心與雞蛋同行。即使你現已成為高牆的磚瓦，我仍盼望你能向港人分享時移勢易、立場轉變的心路歷程，好讓我們了解你最新的法理邏輯。"},{"pid":"fb390a17c0c224a550b999b4f34183cf3e76a423","tid":2454072,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7H4a9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7H4a9T.jpg&h=f8e1976f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"068d3130b479124a430d6bbf09f0cfcd23d8ce48","tid":2454072,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxsAP3r.jpg&amp;h=0b824843&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"1cae9671115f1d9986aee7c1f0cbc3626065f5e1","tid":2454072,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"泛民不嬲都愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iY4RABG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiY4RABG.png&h=110e1443&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66943f77d61c2828423580dd1f0cbc85401ee745","tid":2454072,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8358f1f890dd4e67898094c04bd7ee9269c314f","tid":2454072,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:07:36.000Z","msg":"當日初選都話睇唔到有犯國安法<br />\n11哥根本無料到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"法律專業知識話俾佢知冇,但法律專業知識敵唔過奶共意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}